Title: Fix host rename for hosts with parents in same folder
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: wato
Date: 1677338904
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0p23

If you renamed a host which was a parent of another host in the same folder,
the parent was correctly renamed but the host itself was not.

A workarround was to rename the host twice.
